{"tid":937602,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩同上司一齊走，佢突然話鍾意我","createTime":"2018-12-11T16:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T16:17:27.000Z","uid":61543,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4d0caac13838d3d7220f543bf67ec7f6e652d43d","tid":937602,"uid":61543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T16:07:29.000Z","msg":"我同上司ot，ot一齊走<br />\n本身傾緊project既野<br />\n佢就話有其他野煩，然後突然講：其實我好鍾意你<br />\n我：多謝，第一次上司生咁同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢：我講緊既係想拖你隻手想攬住你個隻鍾意你喎<br />\n我：下 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後dead air左30秒，佢無啦啦係到笑：你既反應好搞笑<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪拎呢d黎講笑<br />\n佢：我好認真，但我都係想同你講下，唔洗太上心<br />\n<br />\n然後佢就講其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後我而家諗返覺得成件事好撚怪<br />\n即係我唔洗回應佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n扮冇野會唔會唔係幾好"},{"pid":"0534b310a1f0a24e2e8131b5fbefc308d45e5b62","tid":937602,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T16:08:01.000Z","msg":"你啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩用"},{"pid":"e0a70cb1b2995b31809fc6b5178fe98b741ca8c0","tid":937602,"uid":187076,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T16:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8B5rjb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8B5rjb.jpg&h=d75d81ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4eb5fd5ddaffd157a48fe7d6493470494eaeb45c","tid":937602,"uid":64601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T16:09:08.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣嘅po都要抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1322dcc70aa9f10baf9bc22b06c2f727c871fd5","tid":937602,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T16:09:24.000Z","msg":"大抄post時代"},{"pid":"111ce78032cce2d84955f8592343f3d0ac93ccc3","tid":937602,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1322dcc70aa9f10baf9bc22b06c2f727c871fd5","tid":937602,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T16:09:24.000Z","msg":"大抄post時代"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T16:09:45.000Z","msg":"XX?"},{"pid":"c2b5719c77afb0865936e9fe2a73b4a6051bea80","tid":937602,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"111ce78032cce2d84955f8592343f3d0ac93ccc3","tid":937602,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1322dcc70aa9f10baf9bc22b06c2f727c871fd5","tid":937602,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T16:09:24.000Z","msg":"大抄post時代"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T16:09:45.000Z","msg":"XX?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T16:10:52.000Z","msg":"咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27324841e67cef73ecb395d35abe75b3124d5755","tid":937602,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2b5719c77afb0865936e9fe2a73b4a6051bea80","tid":937602,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"111ce78032cce2d84955f8592343f3d0ac93ccc3","tid":937602,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1322dcc70aa9f10baf9bc22b06c2f727c871fd5","tid":937602,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T16:09:24.000Z","msg":"大抄post時代"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T16:09:45.000Z","msg":"XX?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T16:10:52.000Z","msg":"咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T16:12:39.000Z","msg":"XX?<img src